snippet.title: Irem Arcade Classics (Sega Saturn JPN)
snippet.description: Retro pack of Spartan X, Zippy Race and Ten Yard Fight. You may know Spartan X better as the classic Kung Fu for NES. Short clips of all three games are shown.
